spath; generated tests should prefer the 9.x default Rest5-based ElasticsearchClient.of(...) path or pure model/mapper coverage rather than importing org.elasticsearch.client.RestClient.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0f75385da09c8c71016a40d24007488193a3bd53df7bec64a2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2666, "output": 699, "cacheRead": 55808, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 59173, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782633013895, "responseId": "resp_0f75385da09c8c71016a40d23680948193a0f927ba942fd23b"}}
